68a5dba4c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jordan Lund \u003cjlund@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1499265 - Intermittent failure in update-verify: Task timeout after 3600 seconds. Force killing container. r=aki\n\nIntermittent failure in update-verify: Task timeout after 3600 seconds. Force killing container\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8925", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/release-update-verify/kind.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b022e81e18232fa351c5fbf4b5b59f1102eb2477", "parents": ["1273c0362dd7a7afe2ccc06514f8238d16d057f1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gijs Kruitbosch \u003cgijskruitbosch@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1497443 - set min-width to auto for flexed buttons in the prefs, r=jaws\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8387", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/incontentprefs/preferences.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "59b646e9e8990e8655568896885857c7fb0fc676", "parents": ["b022e81e18232fa351c5fbf4b5b59f1102eb2477"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500238 correct expected result for monoPanningNoop tests r=padenot\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9210", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/test/test_stereoPannerNode.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cc7ddb5861a8de34ad979db33ebb46ff1bbfd8c5", "parents": ["59b646e9e8990e8655568896885857c7fb0fc676"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500238 output null from StereoPannerNode when input is null r=padenot\n\nThis is necessary for efficient processing of silence, and is consistent with\nbehavior of other nodes.\n\nA null block current has a single channel of silence, which isn't aligned with\nthe current spec, but is consistent with the direction of\nhttps://github.com/WebAudio/web-audio-api/issues/1471#issuecomment-405668690\n\nDepends on D9210\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9211", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/StereoPannerNode.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "17f777b161890b63b207c412549e4afc7129fa32", "parents": ["cc7ddb5861a8de34ad979db33ebb46ff1bbfd8c5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500238 correct mono-to-stereo panning at centre position r=padenot\n\nand re-use input buffer instead of copying.\n\nDepends on D9211\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9212", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/AudioBlock.h", "dom/media/webaudio/PannerNode.cpp", "dom/media/webaudio/PanningUtils.h", "dom/media/webaudio/StereoPannerNode.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "01b1f806550b9a8c610c653b842305e1f3e9ad3a", "parents": ["17f777b161890b63b207c412549e4afc7129fa32"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500303 correct expected result for stereoPanningWithGain tests r=padenot\n\nDepends on D9212\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9213", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/test/test_stereoPannerNode.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "75d951d7f8acedb2ebd986a4b8668d0bc54f2515", "parents": ["01b1f806550b9a8c610c653b842305e1f3e9ad3a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500303 apply input gain correctly for stereo-to-stereo StereoPanner r=padenot\n\nThe gains passed to GainStereoToStereo() are applied on only one of the input channels.\n\nDepends on D9213\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9214", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/PannerNode.cpp", "dom/media/webaudio/PanningUtils.h", "dom/media/webaudio/StereoPannerNode.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "34266803222fc5017d3aaf900cc12c7554de1646", "parents": ["75d951d7f8acedb2ebd986a4b8668d0bc54f2515"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ehsan Akhgari \u003cehsan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1499918 - Strip URLs reported to the console by the anti-tracking module of any username/password r=baku\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9055", "files": ["toolkit/components/antitracking/AntiTrackingCommon.cpp", "xpcom/build/Services.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bf00005608fd51638394add485699675ce361aa3", "parents": ["34266803222fc5017d3aaf900cc12c7554de1646"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brian Hackett \u003cbhackett1024@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1495910 - Add telemetry for record/replay menu items, r=lsmyth,janerik.", "files": ["devtools/client/webreplay/menu.js", "toolkit/components/telemetry/Scalars.yaml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "040f0e314fcf3251acc978a87a9597c8f25983d1", "parents": ["ce6fcc65a415d3bee52757e3d5a97216ad27daa7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Florian Qu\u00e8ze \u003cflorian@queze.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500482 - Use performance.svg as the about:performance favicon, r=felipe.", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/icons/performance.svg", "browser/themes/shared/jar.inc.mn", "browser/themes/shared/menupanel.inc.css", "toolkit/components/aboutperformance/content/aboutPerformance.xhtml", "toolkit/themes/shared/icons/performance.svg", "toolkit/themes/shared/jar.inc.mn"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a254c5207ba052f56527ea28d3dad50e0182cd33", "parents": ["040f0e314fcf3251acc978a87a9597c8f25983d1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jed Davis \u003cjld@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1498765 - Clean up ContentParent::KillHard handling.  r=mccr8\n\nMessageChannel shouldn't need to care about PContent-specific details.", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "dom/ipc/Content