for publicly accessible\nfiles content:// URIs are more trouble than they're worth.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9420", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/IntentHelper.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2cbb3d6f52b09d55770daf277c509e087d88846d", "parents": ["0df77c2cce9ffeedc5ff7849e6f1145f51312eee"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matthew Noorenberghe \u003cmozilla@noorenberghe.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501552 - Link directly to permission preferences from web notifications. r=jaws, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9619", "files": ["browser/components/nsBrowserGlue.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "221f5453ccfb8c5aa7c9f5f632b9b4fc65e08059", "parents": ["2cbb3d6f52b09d55770daf277c509e087d88846d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540427357, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10032": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nbe -\u003e b9fbb3c00940\nbn-BD -\u003e 029ee4bf2aa8\nbr -\u003e 724a70039d50", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f276cdee219012cc67ac83cb1687cf3d9ea3011a", "parents": ["221f5453ccfb8c5aa7c9f5f632b9b4fc65e08059"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nar -\u003e 0da123dd637a\nbe -\u003e 08c48519ca7e\nbn-BD -\u003e 029ee4bf2aa8\nbr -\u003e 724a70039d50", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4d53e56a539190350aa5805320d75f787769b6fd", "parents": ["f276cdee219012cc67ac83cb1687cf3d9ea3011a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540429227, "git_c