ion window, OnActivate is called.  When using\nWindows 8, 2nd parameter (IInspectable) might be nullptr.\n\nSo when this parameter is nullptr, it should recognize as alertclickcallback\nwith mClickable=true.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8076", "files": ["widget/windows/ToastNotificationHandler.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "48cbfa94559ec1167ed3d31f55bd025fd19b91fe", "parents": ["7f4bdb3b9a35fb04365daaf9b3d2077255efe280"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dragos Crisan  \u003cdcrisan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501250 - Intermittent [worker:error] distutils.errors.DistutilsFileError: cannot copy tree '/builds/worker/artifacts': not a directory. r=pmoore, a=test-only", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/mozharness_test.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b2d0036536466f8bb4e7c32be967fe2c428924f4", "parents": ["48cbfa94559ec1167ed3d31f55bd025fd19b91fe"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Julian Descottes \u003cjdescottes@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501622 - Cleanup CSS variable preview tooltip content when hovering new variable. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9648", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/rules/test/browser_rules_variables_01.js", "devtools/client/shared/widgets/tooltip/VariableTooltipHelper.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2f826495a5ecca19b042ff704e97ee814dd81402", "parents": ["b2d0036536466f8bb4e7c32be967fe2c428924f4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nathan Froyd \u003cfroydnj@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501523 - Part 1: Externalize jpeg_nbits_table from jpeg_nbits_table.h. r=aosmond, a=RyanVM\n\nThe current setup means that including jpeg_nbits_table.h creates a 64K\nstatic table in the current compilation unit...for every inclusion of\njpeg_nbits_table.h.  Since we have two such inclusions, we have two\ncopies of this table, and the linker is not merging them; perhaps there\nis a limit on the size of identical blobs of data it will merge.\n\nIn any event, this setup is suboptimal; instead, we should have a single\ninstance of jpeg_nbits_table in some external source file, and the\nheader can declare it like any other variable.", "files": ["media/libjpeg/externalize-table.diff", "media/libjpeg/jpeg_nbits_table.c", "media/libjpeg/jpeg_nbits_table.h", "media/libjpeg/moz.build", "media/update-libjpeg.sh"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0203e34e995060ce1fb3abbe5c5b6f8b2fc76ba7", "parents": ["2f826495a5ecca19b042ff704e97ee814dd81402"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nathan Froyd \u003cfroydnj@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501523 - Part 2: Remove separate jpeg_nbits_table copies from assembly files. r=aosmond, a=RyanVM\n\nContinuing the theme from the first part, the optimized assembly files\nfor x86-64 and i386 include their own private copies of\njpeg_nbits_table.  There's no need for them to do so; they can make use\nof the C copy that we commonized in the first patch.", "files": ["media/libjpeg/assembly-tables.diff", "media/libjpeg/simd/i386/jchuff-sse2.asm", "media/libjpeg/simd/x86_64/jchuff-sse2.asm", "media/update-libjpeg.sh"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "218a57067843f6f7a587363ee2799bf7a317eeca", "parents": ["0203e34e995060ce1fb3abbe5c5b6f8b2fc76ba7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ehsan Akhgari \u003cehsan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501657 - Move early betas to use the strict list for the default cookie restrictions. r=francois, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9657", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6accf3af8c85e682f27dbb243c141eb94c077dc6", "parents": ["218a57067843f6f7a587363ee2799bf7a317eeca"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_64_0b4_BUILD1", "FENNEC_64_0b4_BUILD1", "FIREFOX_64_0b4_BUILD1"]}], "date": 1540478107, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10038": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 6accf3af8c85e682f27dbb243c141eb94c077dc6 with FENNEC_64_0b4_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "771ec2085c4a659cf51bcf044a3195082bbbb5a3", "parents": ["6accf3af8c85e682f27dbb243c141eb94c077dc6"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540490060, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10039": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 6accf3af8c85e682f27dbb243c141eb94c077dc6 with FIREFOX_64_0b4_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e5f7a3cee61857a847f19ed1157d0769f77df6b1", "parents": ["771ec2085c4a659cf51bcf044a3195082bbbb5a3"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540490291, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10040": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 6accf3af8c85e682f27dbb243c141eb94c077dc6 with DEVEDITION_64_0b4_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8b00dab19f57a93b94603a7d889a1d684d897178", "parents": ["e5f7a3cee61857a847f19ed1157d0769f77df6b1"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540490461, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10041": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jordan Lund \u003cjlund@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1502234 - beta l10n is broken for locale be, manually updating l10n-changesets, r=bustage a=testing", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "aeac14f57e9a41301655ae8b488c8a2563d2b615", "parents": ["8b