y could return NS_BASE_STREAM_WOULD_BLOCK.\nIn this case we want to retry reading from the input stream.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9900", "files": ["netwerk/test/unit/test_alt-data_simple.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7e5a43957be53451b2d48e536f3e8d0b95bd6d8f", "parents": ["67afcd6169b82d3d3c1bfa7524034519c997b1a7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matthew Gaudet \u003cmgaudet@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1496750 - Always re-mark JIT code as executable in AutoWritableJitCodeFallible. r=jandem, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/jit/JitRealm.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fa02a3cb47228ee873efc02896707b77a5bdf7d8", "parents": ["7e5a43957be53451b2d48e536f3e8d0b95bd6d8f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alex Chronopoulos \u003cachronop@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1501605 - Update cubeb from upstream to 04d58b6. r=kinetik, a=RyanVM", "files": ["media/libcubeb/README_MOZILLA", "media/libcubeb/include/cubeb.h", "media/libcubeb/src/cubeb_audiounit.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "08d5049ad5d9690ed1f80409a58a9d58415437e6", "parents": ["fa02a3cb47228ee873efc02896707b77a5bdf7d8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1493742 - When accepting a layout viewport update from the main thread, constrain its position to enclose the visual viewport. r=kats, a=RyanVM\n\nAPZ wants the *size* of the layout viewport from the main thread, but it\nknows the position better.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9448", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/src/AsyncPanZoomController.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "805ba967bcb5ad545958544a1ad0206d900a3fe8", "parents": ["08d5049ad5d9690ed1f80409a58a9d58415437e6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daisuke Akatsuka \u003cdakatsuka@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500833 - Avoid updating if added animation was already removed. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9616", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/animation/animation.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2e302b256039185f559d5ac6f621783bc83cbfa5", "parents": ["805ba967bcb5ad545958544a1ad0206d900a3fe8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daisuke Akatsuka \u003cdakatsuka@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500833 - Add a test which adds animation then immediately removes that. r=pbro, a=RyanVM\n\nDepends on D9616\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9617", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/animation/test/browser.ini", "devtools/client/inspector/animation/test/browser_animation_logic_mutations_add_remove_immediately.js", "devtools/client/inspector/animation/test/doc_mutations_add_remove_immediately.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "52d060761f0c9edacbcc7476b7d6ec919d9ce986", "parents": ["2e302b256039185f559d5ac6f621783bc83cbfa5"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540819937, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10059": {"changesets": [{"author": "D\u00e3o Gottwald \u003cdao@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1502096 - Make peviewing and selecting the default theme work consistently in Dark mode. r=spohl, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9861", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/extensions/LightweightThemeManager.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "869a690e1c28c9baf1700cbe0100d58b282b008e", "parents": ["52d060761f0c9edacbcc7476b7d6ec919d9ce986"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Valentin Gosu \u003cvalentin.gosu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1500861 - Add shutdownWithTimeout method to nsIThreadPool. r=froydnj,erahm, a=RyanVM\n\nThis method is necessary because some threads might be stuck making blocking\ncalls. This means the thread is not processing any events, and we're unable\nto safely terminate it. Our solution here is to leak the stuck threads\ninstead of waiting for them and potentially causing a shutdown hang.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9601", "files": ["netwerk/dns/nsHostResolver.cpp", "xpcom/tests/gtest/TestThreadPool.cpp", "xpcom/threads/nsIThreadPool.idl", "xpcom/threads/nsThread.h", "xpcom/threads/nsThreadPool.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "442e20f46b5d670b0dafb158072dadde45d58e23", "parents": ["869a690e1c28c9baf1700cbe0100d58b282b008e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1502658 - Remove SVG use attribute change handling code from nsSVGUseFrame to SVGUseElement. r=longsonr, a=RyanVM\n\nMost of those shouldn't rely on a frame to run.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9996", "files": ["dom/svg/SVGUseElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGUseElement.h", "layout/svg/nsSVGUseFrame.cpp", "layout/svg/nsSVGUseFrame.h", "testing/web-platform/tests/svg/linking/reftests/use-hidden-attr-change.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c28a4c172db8362c9c66fe788484b6083d46b0c8", "parents": ["442e20f46b5d670b0dafb158072dadde45d58e23"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540822392, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10060": {"changesets": [{"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1493976 - Reset the resolution to 1 when entering fullscreen mode. r=kats,xidorn, a=RyanVM\n\nThe previous resolution is restored when exiting fullscreen mode.\n\nDepends on D9442\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9443", "files": ["dom/base/nsDocument.cpp", "dom/base/nsIDocument.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cbd3baf67f7fe586c281032fe4b2e0ae83b3daa3", "parents": ["c28a4c172db8362c9c66fe788484b6083d46b0c8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gijs Kruitbosch \u003cgijskruitbosch@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1491333 - Make findbarClose test less clownshoes. r=florian, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D9633", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/general/browser_findbarClose.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "60872ce3bd7d8ffc70e566f77bdc4ccdc7e2585b", "parents": ["cbd3baf67f7fe586c281032fe4b2e0ae83b3daa3"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_64_0b5_BUILD1", "DEVEDITION_64_0b5_RELEASE", "FENNEC_64_0b5_BUILD1", "FENNEC_64_0b5_RELEASE", "FIREFOX_64_0b5_BUILD1", "FIREFOX_64_0b5_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1540831536, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10061": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 60872ce3bd7d8ffc70e566f77bdc4ccdc7e2585b with FIREFOX_64_0b5_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5ed332f28da84b19c97f894ea47208c3f021e7de", "parents": ["60872ce3bd7d8ffc70e566f77bdc4ccdc7e2585b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540836651, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10062": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 60872ce3bd7d8ffc70e566f77bdc4ccdc7e2585b with DEVEDITION_64_0b5_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0ac84a90581f0173bed17da5cdcda3a0b8c46769", "parents": ["5ed332f28da84b19c97f894ea47208c3f021e7de"], "tags": []}], "date": 1540836824, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10063": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 60872ce3bd7d8ffc70e566f77bdc4ccdc7e2585b with FENNEC_64_0b5_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE