003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1494549 - Disable new aboutdebugging tests on Linux 32;r=ladybenko\n\nDepends on D8513\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8961", "files": ["devtools/client/aboutdebugging-new/test/browser/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "177dda6727faf35ed3ed5dd4bf92199cc441b270", "parents": ["51bea90a7500096e998b81000a9f766487753e62"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Tolfsen \u003cato@sny.no\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1499057: webdriver: remove known web element cache; r=whimboo\n\nThe known web element cache in the WebDriver test client, or\nwebdriver.Session._element_cache, is used only to avoid constructing\nnew webdriver.Element instances of the same web element and serves\nno practical purpose beyond that\n\nSince this client is intended for testing purposes, we would like\nto be able to construct duplicate webdriver.Element instances,\nso that e.g. fake elements can be constructed and send to the remote end.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8855", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/tools/webdriver/webdriver/client.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5df04b130a16afcaa917204055b8227f1ef0f411", "parents": ["177dda6727faf35ed3ed5dd4bf92199cc441b270"], "tags": []}, {"author": "yulia \u003cystartsev@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1488375 - Use target.getFront to instantiate MemoryFront; r=ochameau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D7097", "files": ["devtools/client/memory/panel.js", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/memory-helpers.js", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_memory.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_memory_allocations_01.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_memory_allocations_02.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_memory_allocations_03.html", "devtools/server/tests/mochitest/test_memory_allocations_04.html", "d