 for logging stability checks. , a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-testsUse tbpl formatter for logging stability checks. (#13520)\n\nBefore we were using the default formatter, which was a problem after changing to\nthe low-output GroupingFormatter since we were seeing no output and causing CI to believe\nthe job had stopped.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 486e94e16f05cf435781ab8f55ad4347ce57dba1\nwpt-pr: 13520\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/tools/ci/check_stability.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d86ff2a812498676e62c43e439413eead4a15c2c", "parents": ["6fd480efffe2607a79668e405ffa4feda045dd9f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Farre \u003cfarre@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1480198 [wpt PR 13495] - [Gecko Bug 1480198] Check for allowed patterns deeper in LSAN stack., a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-testsCheck for allowed patterns deeper in LSAN stack.\n\nAdd the property lsan-max-stack-depth to enable configuring how many\nstack frames we allow LSANLeaks to record.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D8192\n\nbugzilla-url: https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1480198\ngecko-commit: a0702430e839a7e0b1ea1dc78927d38ede1a007a\ngecko-integration-branch: central\ngecko-reviewers: jgraham\n\n--\nFix lint.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 02e9e6a6ecb6693f6eea79ec21f66a577d0a6e12, 617f510a05620b785bf6d6e178ff41b0dfb8960e\nwpt-pr: 13495\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/tools/wptrunner/wptrunner/tests/test_wpttest.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9d5ffc2c0617c039aa45911628f020cb5cf191af", "parents": ["d86ff2a812498676e62c43e439413eead4a15c2c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1499111 - [wpt-sync] Update web-platform-tests to 37d83def16bacfa66abac065f8f5adc8f7e7a4fc, a=testonly\n\nwpt-head: 37d83def16bacfa66abac065f8f5adc8f7e7a4fc\nwpt-type: landing\n", "files": ["t